   -----+-----+-----+-----+-----+           -----+-----+-----+-----+-----+
   w'x' |  0  |  0  |  1  |  1  |           w'x' |  0  |  0  |  0  |  1  |
        +-----+-----+-----+-----+                +-----+-----+-----+-----+
   w'x  |  0  |  1  |  0  |  0  |           w'x  |  0  |  0  |  0  |  0  |
        +-----+-----+-----+-----+                +-----+-----+-----+-----+
