d) For each Boolean function, give the minimized sum of products expression.

   P() = w'y'z + x'yz' + xy'z' + wy'd'

   a() = 1

   b() = w'x'z + w'x'y + x'yz + xy'

   c() = w'x'y + w'y' + w

   d() = w'x'y + x'z' + w'z

   e() = x'z'

   f() = w'xy' + wx'

   g() = xy' + wy' + w'x'y +x'yz'

